      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper does not mention Conda or any package manager. It mentions 'minimal set of dependencies' and names specific libraries (Django, Celery, Numpy/SciPy, JavaScript, D3.js, pymzML, PostgreSQL) but does not reference Conda.",
