        "The card frames the task as reconstructing a 'molecular network export step' that produces a GraphML artifact, but the paper describes ms2lda.org as a web application with interactive visualization. The paper does not document any GraphML export functionality or network file export mechanism.",
        "The research question emphasizes 'spectral similarity relationships' as the basis for network edges, but the paper describes edges as representing 'connections between molecules and Mass2Motifs (above a certain threshold)' \u2014 a different relationship model based on motif membership rather than spectral similarity.",
