    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/mass2motif-annotation-mapping/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Ms2lda.org also includes a growing library of pre-annotated Mass2Motifs from the Massbank and GNPS data sets (van der Hooft et al., 2016) for matching and decomposition. As a new feature, we offer matching functionality which allows users to compare the Mass2Motifs found in their data with those in our growing database of (often annotated) Mass2Motifs.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes Mass2Motif matching and annotation via database comparison, but does NOT mention Spec2Vec as the similarity metric. Paper uses 'matching functionality' against a database of annotated Mass2Motifs, not Spec2Vec similarity scoring. The functional goal (annotation mapping) is present, but the specific tool (Spec2Vec) is not named or evidenced in the passages.",
