      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Python is used for MS2LDA implementation and that variational inference (the algorithm for LDA) is implemented in Numpy/SciPy. However, the paper does not explicitly mention logging convergence metrics or plotting convergence curves as part of the MS2LDA workflow described.",
