      "asbval:note": "Paper describes motif-matching functionality against a database of pre-annotated Mass2Motifs (from Massbank and GNPS), but does NOT mention MassQL or MotifDB by name. The paper performs motif matching/comparison but uses different named resources (Massbank, GNPS) rather than the claimed MotifDB and MassQL tools.",
