      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "we offer matching functionality which allows users to compare the Mass2Motifs found in their data with those in our growing database of (often annotated) Mass2Motifs. Users can view candidate matches and link Mass2Motifs where they agree with the match. When linked, annotations are transferred between matched pairs. Ms2lda.org also includes a growing library of pre-annotated Mass2Motifs from the Massbank and GNPS data sets",
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes motif matching and annotation workflow, but the reference database is Massbank and GNPS, not MotifDB. The functional workflow (MS2LDA \u2192 motif matching \u2192 annotation) is correct, but the named database resource differs.",
