      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Ms2lda.org also includes a growing library of pre-annotated Mass2Motifs from the Massbank and GNPS data sets (van der Hooft et al., 2016) for matching and decomposition. As a new feature, we offer matching functionality which allows users to compare the Mass2Motifs found in their data with those in our growing database of (often annotated) Mass2Motifs. Users can view candidate matches and link Mass2Motifs where they agree with the match.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes Mass2Motif matching and annotation functionality, but does NOT mention MassQL or MotifDB by name. The paper describes a matching feature that compares discovered Mass2Motifs against a database of pre-annotated Mass2Motifs, which is functionally similar but uses different named tools/databases than claimed.",
