      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MS2LDA decomposes each molecule into sets of Mass2Motifs... a method inspired by text modelling, to decompose fragmentation spectra into sets of conserved fragment and neutral loss features (called Mass2Motifs)",
